      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3611 - It is narrated from Jamil ibn Darraj, from Abu Abdullah (as):\n\"Allah (swt), the Almighty and Glorious, does not close a door of sustenance for a believer except that He opens for him what is better than it.\""
